com.n9mtq4.logwindow.listener

Interface ListenerAttribute

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    AdditionListener, ConsoleListener, DisableListener, EnableListener, GenericListener, ObjectListener, RemovalListener
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    History, ModuleExit, ModuleJarLoader, ModuleListener, StdOutRedirection

    public interface ListenerAttribute
    Created by will on 8/13/15 at 3:42 PM.
    This interface is extended by AdditionListener, EnableListener, ObjectListener, DisableListener, and RemovalListener. This interface's only job is to allow multiple types to be passed to a method.
    Since:
    v5.0
    See Also:
    AdditionListener, EnableListener, ObjectListener, DisableListener, RemovalListener
